{"title":"Clase introducción-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/General/Clase introducción-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"- Clase\\Nintroducción","guid":"5ExIDlTXRjWZFMfLvX1YvA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Desarrollo de la\\NGeriatría y Gerontología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Inicios internacionales:","guid":"ghDTn05ZG67N7u6BkesYmg","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"Francia (1939) → Primera sociedad geriátrica.","guid":"WXle-EldKW7IuAqsDR7Mfg","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"EE.UU. (1942).","guid":"1NlZRMWiHJVrf3sZCPqrsw","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"Argentina (1945) → Primera en Latinoamérica.","guid":"eGxUi_1mV7qDmSTt_CbGcQ","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"2","text":"España (1948).","guid":"AzIN6m-3WxdSC8juLvziWA","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"2","text":"Reino Unido (1959).","guid":"wXqkvYdYzVjyRCpkcPeTFA","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"Desarrollo en Chile:","guid":"-t1jRmUFBCMXljlrVNsw1Q","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"Grupo de Estudios Gerontológicos (1990) → Primera organización.","guid":"C6Yjtqb7zB9-n4RoKJGoOg","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"8","text":"Sociedad Chilena de Geriatría y Gerontología (1993) → Creada ~60 años después de Francia.","guid":"K7ndh-2F8iPjo5AW5zbu2g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"0","text":"Definición: Geriatría\\Nvs. Gerontología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"Geriatría:","guid":"NY8qAELVGVYAn5xql73gRQ","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"Rama de la medicina.","guid":"n4OIkMIpwuO2C9uMy-jGtQ","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"12","text":"Enfocada en la salud de adultos mayores.","guid":"RRH-hOTaoYnuK7ZSDd3-3g","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"11","text":"Gerontología:","guid":"fcB6u80-jN6cTlnkcehoeg","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"Estudio del envejecimiento.","guid":"IFyDij5w4Hi0_qbkxP5P6g","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"Multidisciplinaria (filosofía, psicología, ciencias sociales).","guid":"9nXaHpIEicvFMzZ4F-lHJw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"0","text":"Historia en Chile","guid":"","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"1997: Primera beca directa en geriatría (U. de Chile).","guid":"vzZagmFp8025vvh0gVQVSg","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"2003: Reconocimiento como especialidad médica.","guid":"GHlCz3yRnx-905vBe6X_Cg","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"18","text":"2005: U. Mayor inicia formación en geriatría.","guid":"m9-dY3p25GBoK5pdnT7AFw","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"18","text":"2022: Solo 162 geriatras registrados en Chile.","guid":"N7kF0VOdL7MO8IVjQ9ooRg","children":[]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"0","text":"Brecha de Geriatras\\Nen Chile","guid":"7LNxTCy5FnibNKlhWsMR0Q","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"Situación actual:","guid":"mfP5evgMtlJuwt2ulStszA","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"1 geriatra/15.000 personas mayores.","guid":"XsU-kZiqo4zhfNZjAb_FDw","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"23","text":"Meta ideal: 1 geriatra/5.000 personas mayores.","guid":"2EMgTDblpOPy8DbgM9AGww","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"23","text":"Déficit: Se requieren 4-5 veces más geriatras → 589 geriatras a nivel nacional.","guid":"6swg0KvhpIEHqqFqX1gkUg","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"23","text":"Proyección:","guid":"JCOEKg3a-bnjnnlT4ugd9w","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"Con el ritmo actual → No se alcanzará en 100 años (n).","guid":"Ou-5w5KdwrlrbXEmvG47eA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"0","text":"Rol del Geriatra\\Nen Chile","guid":"lWabJZVCcsmuBc62A2NUTA","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"Actual:","guid":"5V5QaiOGAVnOU7Cqdc1KvA","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"Rol formador.","guid":"CAGNYhqnByS69gTggHIKIA","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"Desarrollo de política pública.","guid":"DMIqG2o4namMsZtoUVq0EA","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"31","text":"Gestión e inspiración.","guid":"66O2DCeRInvPOK3FgwMonw","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"31","text":"Consultoría → En vez de cubrir todas las necesidades asistenciales (n).","guid":"4Tc8md2Fb7bughCqq5Djyw","children":[]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"30","text":"Desafíos:","guid":"bGz6AmekDLNinTmf6Kuv9w","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"Implementar modelos de atención geriátrica.","guid":"C1VGw5WEcBTR6WnKf90g2A","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"Formar y motivar a hospitales para adoptar estos modelos en el sector público.","guid":"75EBOUEXQHyko6fFspMsgw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"0","text":"Origen de la\\NGeriatría Moderna","guid":"","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"Marjorie Warren:","guid":"k_AnQq7aisn6n9CNfZ711A","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"Base de la geriatría moderna.","guid":"XsSWib0s8N05Y3JlNFRGpg","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"Hospital en Londres (S. XX) → Camas llenas de personas mayores con enfermedades crónicas.","guid":"A75mLy2EKaVe5gVWRVydtg","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"40","text":"Intervención: Implementó rehabilitación y atención centrada en personas mayores.","guid":"0visJE2uhsi7q_BZNIhI2A","children":[]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"39","text":"Publicación clave:","guid":"iJgg5NCrlnI4oE-TJpoXUA","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"The Lancet (1946) → Primer paper sobre el cuidado de personas mayores con enfermedades crónicas (n).","guid":"dHCGq_TtqhnQi-EjRNR4Ww","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"0","text":"Relevancia Actual y\\NFuturo de la Geriatría","guid":"","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"Cambio demográfico:","guid":"ZbIhNhxIpVckpoiISyeEnw","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"Aumento sostenido en el envejecimiento poblacional.","guid":"CUEVND44_WAlaYIhB-rd3Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"Familia/sociedad: No pueden proporcionar el cuidado necesario en casa debido a las obligaciones laborales.","guid":"X9Os_n4uGpcp92b6XIn_AQ","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"46","text":"Falta de establecimientos de larga estadía → Pacientes permanecen en hospitales → Pacientes sociosanitarios (n).","guid":"IKBU_l5xwUZAA6YqZW3vyQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"0","text":"Rol de la Geriatría:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"Recuperación funcional de personas mayores.","guid":"O3VPjVl1dXgN3sm3exeTuw","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"51","text":"Reinserción en sus hogares con tratamiento de enfermedades crónicas + rehabilitación (n).","guid":"UbMb72ESjZsdtpt9Rd3Uxg","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"0","text":"Principales Recomendaciones\\N(Marjorie Warren)","guid":"eJotZ3Ho5ww6DaQYTUnWrA","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"Adaptación del ambiente\\Nal paciente mayor:","guid":"Wyf1IEUxNhBSfMrbQNoWVw","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"Modificaciones para mantener\\Nindependencia:","guid":"YXnbaHcjU2MMAZr2arrwnA","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"Pasadores.","guid":"NVxQwzFrHRdypc55FS_9wQ","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"Duchas accesibles (sin baranda) + asientos altos.","guid":"L5k3rxydNXNxufzCUDmMrQ","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"56","text":"Apoyos para el baño.","guid":"ew72ujG9ouw1p3x2NoRGRw","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"56","text":"Mejora del contraste entre suelo/pared → Mejora de movilidad\\N+ prevención de caídas (n).","guid":"CzMYZUOGRi0xm9oCXOY0VA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"54","text":"Programas de\\Nrehabilitación activos:","guid":"JJjTyE9SdX8ixAkaHTMBLw","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"Importancia de rehabilitación\\Nen personas mayores:","guid":"GqogEWDdfcF-qUSeSkNXwA","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"Recuperación funcional.","guid":"QTtcjFzRrTJqfNfbHGNRrA","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"62","text":"Reinserción en la sociedad.","guid":"IgLjQzz5orZdPWgDA3y-qw","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"62","text":"Romper con la visión de \"paciente pasivo\" → Ejercicio y rehabilitación clave en geriatría (n).","guid":"NBz2GWk_AvluN69HaXlG3A","children":[]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"61","text":"Trabajo en equipo:","guid":"E6qnEWCpyjgKOjEGOEN62g","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"Atención geriátrica requiere un equipo multidisciplinario.","guid":"fXqzNHBjQWAafORteImp7g","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"66","text":"Geriatra solo → No es suficiente sin un equipo bien formado (n).","guid":"IiDkTVAkYOQvDfA2LVP8sg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"54","text":"Elementos Clave del\\NEquipo Geriátrico","guid":"L_w_uCz-OiFVdnwJcTecRA","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"Equipo\\Ninterdisciplinario:","guid":"I6YWECN3A6NZBJqPN1C9IQ","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"Médico → Dirige el tratamiento.","guid":"Cc_nUz_zU-UNmu3wK9LKlg","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"Asistente social → Apoyo en aspectos socioeconómicos.","guid":"fOz2m2rYVfQvT4lBMQnstQ","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"70","text":"Enfermera → Cuidado continuo + coordinación.","guid":"VBdY7R2HOIkagzORbsF4_g","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"70","text":"Fonoaudiólogo → Mejora de comunicación y deglución.","guid":"fmS2ShkseC85BNC-e99pfg","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"70","text":"Terapia ocupacional/emocional → Rehabilitación cognitiva y funcional (n).","guid":"CY-5kFOBtSx0aRNtK7Cd3Q","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"70","text":"Kinesiólogo: Mejora funcionalidad.","guid":"c9P_cgINyv4yIGl8fmLFCA","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"70","text":"Nutricionista: Apoyo nutricional.","guid":"P97hBA47MrIUjNU1P9zePw","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"70","text":"Psicólogo: Motivar al paciente a realizar ejercicio y mejorar su estado anímico (n).","guid":"DwYdCG2KWVZcY-c-KeL1rA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"0","text":"Evolución de\\Nla Geriatría","guid":"","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"Desarrollo internacional:","guid":"BP4H6jLvl8hF37egAer-hQ","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"Mayor avance en países de mayores ingresos (EE.UU., Gran Bretaña, España).","guid":"BCDN22M-y5VvlDf7NB0Nkw","children":[]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"79","text":"En Chile → Desarrollo más lento, iniciado hace 20 años, pero con avance progresivo (n).","guid":"ED0FtkUKtAUlVKnXGgztCg","children":[]}]},{"id":"83","parent":"0","text":"Lecciones\\NAprendidas","guid":"Q2Pc4XnJ4lh71SI5c8ZXTQ","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"Heterogeneidad de los\\Npacientes mayores:","guid":"HcftvHUvQOIy9Os6cd9GqQ","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"Factores clave:","guid":"WChUjTeyUL9dGIuyaGVaQw","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"Estado funcional (actividad física, independencia).","guid":"ErZ5a014HsxgoL-oERsvtQ","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"Participación social/comunitaria.","guid":"ZqSW-xmlkGYM-pkzcDRQiw","children":[]}]},{"id":"88","parent":"84","text":"Ejemplo:","guid":"fL0ExAJtNYoCckdNAbsMrg","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"Paciente A: 80 años, sarcopénico, postrado → Manejo diferente.","guid":"bSdFkgFjrKAb5O5oEM1bog","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"88","text":"Paciente B: 80 años, activo, participa en comunidad → Otro enfoque (n).","guid":"JNqwQ3TpiPdIHhjEKPt-Hw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"83","text":"Intervención\\Npersonalizada:","guid":"NVzNUkhR_u4Dpgs0UyS7Dg","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"Adaptación del\\Nmanejo según:","guid":"PYE_0Daa9m5FBAG3UDe5Ow","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"Contexto personal (físico, emocional, social).","guid":"BBMVOiWkwV9hUujwaresNg","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"92","text":"Religión/moral → Consideración de valores personales (n).","guid":"P0pRxm5NgiNa6_zBLHGXWA","children":[]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"91","text":"Manejo Individualizado","guid":"a7p0IQVdC789h10mQ-LIrg","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"No existen \"recetas\" universales.","guid":"b7EuxHbQ6yo9PvL7FIvfBw","children":[]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"91","text":"Se deben establecer metas\\Nindividuales para cada paciente:","guid":"dchvlGqSqHoExWI4eduEzg","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"Identificación de necesidades específicas.","guid":"PQ9cfhqf6NksSCLyOcxhQw","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"97","text":"Planificación de tratamiento en función de las características propias del paciente (n).","guid":"HQ0eYy66aj87h23xUmnrtQ","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"97","text":"Heterogeneidad y Funcionalidad en el Adulto Mayor","guid":"dwxpLT8teSUljqbDNI2o_Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"83","text":"Desarrollo de la\\Nheterogeneidad:","guid":"axk5rRuZDSc0YDuUQoDcKw","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"Al nacer → Todos iguales (funcionamiento estereotipado).","guid":"EDdp2mYYSyhkkzEET4G7oA","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"101","text":"A lo largo de la vida → Factores ambientales, traumas, accidentes,\\Nenfermedades, decisiones y hábitos → Separan trayectorias de vida.","guid":"VGXNTD9_LcZ781L4RBb8EA","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"101","text":"Hábitos:","guid":"Po9RshYqOD5l7VXAe56uMQ","children":[{"id":"105","parent":"104","text":"Decisión de fumar, beber, tener conductas de riesgo\\N→ Impactan en el envejecimiento.","guid":"NlAY8DkyRfNYotsXIgqNEQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"106","parent":"101","text":"Genética: Contribuye solo al 25% de la longevidad,\\Nmientras que 75% depende de los hábitos (n).","guid":"MMohFxI1eLI1aw90Tdc_eg","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"101","text":"Capacidad\\Nfísica/intrínseca:","guid":"Q9ZJuAwO8t9v5GvZeiZiqA","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"Trayectoria óptima:","guid":"QO_i8XDyfWUgQSsvN_xMHw","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"Persona sana, activa físicamente, buena genética → Mantiene funcionalidad alta hasta una etapa avanzada.","guid":"MB_2i0XP0fJsifUcJehmHw","children":[]}]},{"id":"110","parent":"107","text":"Trayectorias alternas:","guid":"MGJ6bHFPV1Ufw-rtQJnkRg","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"Enfermedades crónicas, accidentes → Disminución de la capacidad física antes de lo esperado → Dependencia temprana (n).","guid":"V2eifQRXG_IQG5_mK81vyQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"112","parent":"83","text":"Relevancia de la Edad\\Nvs. Funcionalidad","guid":"H_ApGUR723puTkv0Y8Zy0Q","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"Funcionalidad > Edad:","guid":"RUE40kiHRvEcMO-5A9CKhQ","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"La edad cronológica es menos relevante que la capacidad funcional.","guid":"XrF_LwIeRXl_bzi2D3ugRg","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"113","text":"Importancia de evaluar capacidad funcional para determinar tipo de intervención.","guid":"FFO-KzTaSCpdUt_AVUOhHQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"116","parent":"112","text":"Ejemplo: Persona de 80 años con alta funcionalidad vs. otra de la misma edad con dependencia → Manejo distinto (n).","guid":"JczFj32UCu8NP-08Vey8Gg","children":[]}]},{"id":"117","parent":"83","text":"Enfoque\\Nindividualizado:","guid":"YQ3Dm1tYeKUad09hAP3stA","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"No se puede tratar a todos los adultos mayores de la misma manera.","guid":"UIrOWV4yt85d7NV5FcwHLA","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"117","text":"Necesidad de adaptar las intervenciones según la capacidad funcional y no solo la edad (n).","guid":"Jrn-v3odxTIZnJGxBWt97g","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"117","text":"Funcionalidad como Marcador de Salud","guid":"fDwKrBkLymcU5x40EI_I1w","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"117","text":"Funcionalidad = Principal parámetro para definir intervenciones en geriatría.","guid":"TeYSkXI5_fRl02n0c7LYIA","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"117","text":"Define nivel de intervención y objetivos terapéuticos.","guid":"b84I43MTVzBJn5Q7MzHlxA","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"117","text":"Marcador clave para establecer la severidad de la intervención (\"heroicidad\") que se debe aplicar (n).","guid":"bN05iUV0tnQm-D0RV_ZzNg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"124","parent":"0","text":"División de Pacientes:\\NFuncional vs. No Funcional","guid":"","children":[{"id":"125","parent":"124","text":"Funcional = Autovalente/independiente.","guid":"ZvhTJEKxNP4GKymlDbJR4w","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"124","text":"No funcional = Dependencia en actividades de la vida diaria (AVD).","guid":"PM76MR_Hu1YTHc_ROQsE3Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"127","parent":"0","text":"Definición de Autovalencia vs.\\NAutonomía","guid":"ONOFvSgE7gVJms20BrmYTg","children":[{"id":"128","parent":"127","text":"Autovalente:","guid":"Gj7r-S9uN6l6bHBvCgz03A","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"Independiente en actividades\\Nbásicas de la vida diaria (ABVD):","guid":"IoGO2UQMBKo9PtqgD17IYg","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"Vestirse, alimentarse,\\Nmovilizarse, higiene personal.","guid":"CYC7HmQ3F7FnVTuZao5-ug","children":[]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"128","text":"Paciente físicamente dependiente pero autónomo\\N(e.g., Stephen Hawking):","guid":"dbXr7BJamygI2_8ALolxqg","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"Dependiente físicamente pero\\Ncapaz de tomar decisiones.","guid":"Ol-JLVJ2zLU1Qwn4VJ51Jg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"133","parent":"127","text":"Autónomo:","guid":"P4-QVwHMivprjGtuX2Pkdw","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"Capacidad de tomar decisiones\\Nsobre su vida (capacidad cognitiva):","guid":"CpImUFBQyvRPwwbwcYp5dA","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"Manejo de finanzas, decisiones sobre\\Nmedicamentos, conducción, etc.","guid":"EwH_8lXuMJZ_PMtXT9D6Iw","children":[]}]},{"id":"136","parent":"133","text":"Paciente con\\Ndemencia:","guid":"c7t_ERvqRKIzxVuafTw6MA","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"Puede ser autovalente (capaz de realizar ABVD) pero no\\Nautónomo (incapaz de tomar decisiones complejas).","guid":"ACFcVBsalzNnyrjqP7Dsqw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"127","text":"Pérdida de Funcionalidad\\Nen Demencia","guid":"HOciLVNXJFgfFNEiJ3lIfg","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"Progresión:","guid":"I6fvTG7X2BIZA8HyNqnvPw","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"Pérdida gradual de autonomía → Se agrega pérdida de autovalencia en etapas avanzadas.","guid":"RMYIqBhAjUoGeuliOnv0lQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"141","parent":"0","text":"Reserva Fisiológica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"Definición:","guid":"Kpsocg9W6GNpBWY_ZPqxoA","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"Capacidad del cuerpo para adaptarse a estresores o noxas.","guid":"Yc21GB5IcDc5mSbGY7K5dg","children":[]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"141","text":"Se pierde con el tiempo o con comorbilidades.","guid":"TffqnxhEkMkIGUytQbNpsA","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"141","text":"Impacto en\\NGeriatría:","guid":"NC7VazveqEc-76PgNFAxvw","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"La reserva fisiológica disminuye con la edad → Afecta la capacidad para enfrentar enfermedades o accidentes.","guid":"Vvk_eia6XMp0AR5qc-BhqA","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"145","text":"Cuando la reserva fisiológica cae por debajo de las necesidades metabólicas básicas, sobreviene la muerte (n).","guid":"ehGBIxMV74wbWaomHblwbw","children":[]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"141","text":"Evaluación de la\\NReserva Fisiológica","guid":"Ae3HnzRdbBhUY1-uRrPQRw","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"Aún no existe una forma exacta de medir la reserva fisiológica.","guid":"TJ35YlreSREBL8Tcdzkh1Q","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"148","text":"Se pueden realizar aproximaciones clínicas para evaluar su estado.","guid":"ajUxdGo1KxtcM9N1TALmjA","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"148","text":"Pacientes con menor reserva fisiológica son más vulnerables a complicaciones ante eventos adversos (n).","guid":"CH2bUxXM-jsvtaACVnWF8g","children":[]}]},{"id":"152","parent":"141","text":"Fragilidad y Reserva\\NFisiológica","guid":"LhGLBDfO7K8YKO-iYkBgcA","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"Fragilidad:","guid":"fdLwTQqRsJo-hzYZd-RxcA","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"Pacientes con baja reserva fisiológica → Vulnerables a pequeñas noxas\\N(infecciones, medicamentos).","guid":"c62U91cYk4MWkJIvSqbUcQ","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"153","text":"Un pequeño estímulo (\"empujoncito\") puede generar\\Npérdida de funcionalidad o complicaciones graves.","guid":"HaegJlng4D8VneHgH5VnxQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"156","parent":"152","text":"Pacientes\\Nfrágiles:","guid":"Dj5MWGoBQY5mSTgNWtxFug","children":[{"id":"157","parent":"156","text":"Mayor susceptibilidad a efectos adversos de medicamentos.","guid":"RN-Kn2d4_OlSFWePLxS8Ew","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"156","text":"Un infección urinaria → Puede causar úlceras por decúbito o síndrome confusional agudo (n).","guid":"Ua4oBS5JOwR7F6KfWivDWA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"0","text":"Multimorbilidad en el\\Nadulto mayor:","guid":"YpwvUUjKOOxUaCC0VknESA","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"Solo un 30% de pacientes mayores son \"sanos\".","guid":"H-LMb2r4suQg8Ji5HbW8vQ","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":">36% de los adultos mayores toman 4 o más medicamentos.","guid":"dYpjfl93ztMVmi4tEzIDpA","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"159","text":"La mayoría presenta 3 o más enfermedades crónicas → Complejidad en la atención (n).","guid":"OVivEis4EA0yx2tqR5b7ag","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"159","text":"Ejemplo clínico:","guid":"FTlRnBkQo3cic0ElWhjcOw","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"Paciente con diabetes descompensada, hipertensión severa, EPOC por tabaquismo.","guid":"AImgYHSIqLQJLZhPUjfIZQ","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"163","text":"Además presenta depresión y dificultades para caminar → La combinación de múltiples diagnósticos dificulta el manejo (n).","guid":"ItHjuQRFOu4sY4u9ZugY-Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"166","parent":"0","text":"Enfoque en\\NCalidad de Vida","guid":"","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"Priorizar:","guid":"LxJ9kF0E1QdZD9k9Ea6s4Q","children":[{"id":"168","parent":"167","text":"Conversar con el paciente → Identificar qué problema afecta más su calidad de vida.","guid":"Jc8N9C13-fJn-HEpRbHaYw","children":[]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"166","text":"Enfocar el tratamiento en mejorar ese aspecto prioritario.","guid":"GHCs1gjpCeJjZ5cgDfsQVA","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"166","text":"No es posible \"arreglar todo\" de una vez en pacientes con múltiples enfermedades (n).","guid":"aGDYtXkBxU4hLRP4IbmHyA","children":[]}]},{"id":"171","parent":"0","text":"Desintegración\\Nde Sistemas","guid":"JDnVW1P0f2JpUIMyOXMm9w","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"Pérdida de integración\\Nsistémica:","guid":"bQUi2QvDxFcTjAMzbY7DOg","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"Un problema local puede desencadenar síntomas en otros sistemas.","guid":"AExtDBy5m4I_xoufIx5QxQ","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"172","text":"Ejemplo: Cistitis → Puede causar síndrome confusional agudo.","guid":"IP7WcGwqF10KBmm-UBFUAA","children":[]}]},{"id":"175","parent":"171","text":"La inflamación en un órgano afecta otros sistemas a través de citoquinas y mediadores inflamatorios.","guid":"SS7sZGMWQvthwADhbv36WA","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"171","text":"Todos los sistemas corporales están conectados → Desequilibrio en un sistema afecta al más débil.","guid":"bxjTtnbxbpwP7SsbDiSf6Q","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"171","text":"Los síntomas atípicos en la vejez surgen de la fragilidad en otros sistemas (n).","guid":"EI487Um4cgo0r9S8KP7pww","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"171","text":"Síntomas Atípicos\\Nen la Vejez","guid":"UqF77RgXa9w2-foXOwJUog","children":[{"id":"179","parent":"178","text":"Infección urinaria → Confusión o caídas.","guid":"ERkxKlgnDhBcu9xqNVMGhg","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"178","text":"Neumonía: Puede tener poca tos o fiebre → Manifestarse con caídas.","guid":"O5Rpjx980fsb5LUwDjXlfA","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"178","text":"Infarto agudo de miocardio (IAM): Sin dolor torácico → Solo náuseas o debilidad.","guid":"YleOf3Hb94VqzP0_cuXLbA","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"178","text":"En pacientes mayores, un signo frecuente de infección por coronavirus → Caídas.","guid":"N5Q92FLer0dJODofSK1vAg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"183","parent":"0","text":"Manejo de Medicación\\Nen el Adulto Mayor","guid":"","children":[{"id":"184","parent":"183","text":"Prevención primaria vs.\\Ntiempo de beneficio:","guid":"YSkbzzrTGf8y7uCqUEHvhQ","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"Medicamentos preventivos (e.g., atorvastatina para prevenir eventos cardiovasculares a largo plazo)\\Nno tienen sentido en pacientes mayores (>80 años).","guid":"diBWZnWLZ4AZ8X_ALbSUPg","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"184","text":"Tiempo para obtener beneficio de estos medicamentos → 20-30 años.","guid":"SGoWx2Mpud92YgNAc2_UHw","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"184","text":"En pacientes de 90 años, no es razonable iniciar\\Nprevención primaria con atorvastatina (n).","guid":"CR3QaXRieMlKkR7pdR5Gjw","children":[]}]},{"id":"188","parent":"183","text":"Diabetes en\\Npacientes frágiles:","guid":"CuELKksKAcszLlfvWwg73g","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"No es necesario un control estricto de la glucosa\\N(e.g., mantener en 120-140 mg/dL).","guid":"McSIm0LcC8ZeZo9ubyv2XA","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"188","text":"En pacientes mayores, es más importante evitar la hipoglicemia →\\NMejor tolerar niveles de glucosa más altos (e.g., 180 mg/dL) (n).","guid":"SAQYpyyV0fpfM3qgTG1xCw","children":[]}]},{"id":"191","parent":"183","text":"Enfoque\\NIndividualizado","guid":"Y98PwjvkdBo-OlylbPzgKw","children":[{"id":"192","parent":"191","text":"Paciente mayor frágil (85 años) con múltiples comorbilidades → Enfoque menos estricto.","guid":"Ia2GNgzVCj9mw9YiF83cnA","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"191","text":"Paciente mayor activo, sano, con buena expectativa de vida →\\NEnfoque más estricto en prevención y control de enfermedades (n).","guid":"AmBxvwC1VeNFgnDaSsqIhg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"194","parent":"0","text":"Unidades Especializadas en\\NGeriatría","guid":"Q56VjRUKB2Vhsfg4dWMeKA","children":[{"id":"195","parent":"194","text":"Hospital de día\\Ngeriátrico:","guid":"MEbs4wjLe45iGya7EXAIsg","children":[{"id":"196","parent":"195","text":"Modelo eficiente y bien estudiado.","guid":"V-YTK0AYh6ZkjxSFH-or0g","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"195","text":"Funciona con alta efectividad en el\\Nmanejo de adultos mayores (n).","guid":"bK5ZoUPCjyVsV5zed49kyw","children":[]}]},{"id":"198","parent":"194","text":"Otros modelos:","guid":"DsyQ8R-F9M1Sl6CpMHoXJw","children":[{"id":"199","parent":"198","text":"Ortogeriatría.","guid":"LFr_DDlbdsxIR_PDLrtwyw","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"198","text":"UVA (Unidad de Valoración Geriátrica).","guid":"OhDMrw3KZJ15hflRHe_ccQ","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"198","text":"ELIAM (Enfermería de enlace y atención domiciliaria geriátrica) (n).","guid":"Sa7YtzfAVfcK7LydefXFmw","children":[]}]},{"id":"202","parent":"194","text":"Geriatría entra en otras especialidades: Cardiogeriatría, Oncogeriatría, Nefrología geriátrica (n).","guid":"bVZtIwZClf5W0rMeb2hX4A","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"194","text":"Unidades Geriátricas\\NAgudas (UGA):","guid":"KXxGHkvXXxQBB7TXLzwBhQ","children":[{"id":"204","parent":"203","text":"10 unidades en Chile (Coquimbo, Talcahuano, etc.).","guid":"c1pcg1BgOFpJYFXJIIqqrw","children":[]}]},{"id":"205","parent":"194","text":"Ortogeriatría → Iniciativa en hospitales, pero aún limitada en impacto (n).","guid":"LnzSGkNCf4U6aVJ8UFv7AA","children":[]}]},{"id":"206","parent":"0","text":"Síndromes Geriátricos\\Ny Pronóstico","guid":"HWEkDSltxMFg1is9V3HwvA","children":[{"id":"207","parent":"206","text":"Síndromes geriátricos → Factores pronósticos más relevantes que la edad.","guid":"NzgpXlpcJI91Yc0uAOcCFQ","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"206","text":"Frecuencia:","guid":"GtzYpBy3-itLLI9JNT1QvQ","children":[{"id":"209","parent":"208","text":"Muy comunes en personas mayores.","guid":"f_39OwDK6lZY_YQhHIcI_w","children":[]}]},{"id":"210","parent":"206","text":"Causan pérdida de funcionalidad, mala calidad de vida y aumentan el riesgo de mortalidad.","guid":"W0835Ux6YZ489DX5ICkLng","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"206","text":"Fragilidad, sarcopenia, y otras condiciones.","guid":"Ehx6hgBOict63MewUqhMCw","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"206","text":"Tratamiento:","guid":"RERELUtyv7Ilk3DwI0PQqg","children":[{"id":"213","parent":"212","text":"No siempre se identifica una causa única.","guid":"JJrnEjQTcxVYXTvaTRuk4A","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"212","text":"Se manejan como entidades complejas con enfoque interdisciplinario (n).","guid":"dJMF-zEcFsUkGTTJeFUYZg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"215","parent":"0","text":"Enfoque Geriátrico\\Ndel Siglo XXI","guid":"SZtLmkDQ8EtwAK1fU92fGw","children":[{"id":"216","parent":"215","text":"Éxitos del siglo XX:","guid":"UCfveF4X0t5lwWQZRLr1cw","children":[{"id":"217","parent":"216","text":"Control de enfermedades agudas e infecciones.","guid":"DzPppAnamOI9EA3aU3gt0Q","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"216","text":"Mejoras en mortalidad infantil y prolongación de la esperanza de vida en Chile.","guid":"VU1YlGKjfsp2u_57SSFYBg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"219","parent":"0","text":"Nuevo desafío:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"220","parent":"219","text":"Mayor esperanza de vida, pero con enfermedades crónicas que afectan la calidad de vida.","guid":"ZLFJyCjcZ_hHhB0PJJAqzQ","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"219","text":"Enfoque en mejorar calidad de vida en vez de solo prolongarla (n).","guid":"NxeaqlwQ8kRkbQkMRh23sw","children":[]}]},{"id":"222","parent":"0","text":"Discapacidad y\\NFuncionalidad","guid":"","children":[{"id":"223","parent":"222","text":"Proceso continuo:","guid":"ZK37LD0oYvF_7avaOftTwA","children":[{"id":"224","parent":"223","text":"Inicia con un estresor → Genera impedimento → Dificulta el funcionamiento → Restringe la actividad diaria.","guid":"HUGUZFrTYkoAGFUXLHV-CA","children":[]}]},{"id":"225","parent":"222","text":"Si es grave, puede llevar a dependencia y, en casos severos, a la muerte (n).","guid":"H8vhu3apqlUDHKvGBH0rgw","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"222","text":"Envejecimiento:","guid":"JrG7GQ16X10cu2SrcE0Gsw","children":[{"id":"227","parent":"226","text":"Produce cambios fisiológicos → Mayor riesgo de enfermedades crónicas y peor pronóstico.","guid":"TktPqAy8EgpEKqXONqy2eg","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"226","text":"Principal marcador de salud en el adulto mayor → Funcionalidad (n).","guid":"W90F032Z0FATGPVzRxJ1_w","children":[]}]},{"id":"229","parent":"222","text":"Evaluación de la\\NFuncionalidad","guid":"P7CNqgZoUB0Bp6TaX3xvZQ","children":[{"id":"230","parent":"229","text":"No existe un solo marcador que mida completamente la funcionalidad del adulto mayor.","guid":"Yv5V7gKIKrkGeqRDR6xRGg","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"229","text":"La Evaluación Geriátrica Integral (EGI) es el estándar de oro → Extensa y comprensiva (n).","guid":"fRH6cgTEUKBj-ZrpHJgMwA","children":[]}]},{"id":"232","parent":"222","text":"Funcionalidad:","guid":"GoFQlg_xHmNmY9tDaMygPg","children":[{"id":"233","parent":"232","text":"Capacidad de realizar actividades de la vida diaria (AVD) de manera independiente y autónoma.","guid":"T2UZdg0G8TlzNbm4dhbUjw","children":[]}]},{"id":"234","parent":"222","text":"Clasificación de AVD:","guid":"HK0wbSqOgREfeVa5eIo2QQ","children":[{"id":"235","parent":"234","text":"Básicas (ABVD):","guid":"Or0_0EIMgeI-8QlyHbuVvg","children":[{"id":"236","parent":"235","text":"Comer, vestirse, higiene personal, traslado, controlar esfínteres.","guid":"KChRYTKSTCw_nKxAZOvjNw","children":[]}]},{"id":"237","parent":"234","text":"Instrumentales (AIVD):","guid":"S9P90mcPi7JjwamsSOX4RA","children":[{"id":"238","parent":"237","text":"Manejar dinero, cocinar, usar teléfono, transporte público.","guid":"RJSsnEVrrbVlZ-bYBEU6Rg","children":[]}]},{"id":"239","parent":"234","text":"Avanzadas:","guid":"VMI1zlizvrwxT8pYb0OGZQ","children":[{"id":"240","parent":"239","text":"Participación social, viajar, conducir, trabajar (n).","guid":"a9PcUke7RJVlfgUEOzj1yA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"241","parent":"222","text":"Escalas de Evaluación\\Nde Funcionalidad","guid":"ZQtGySnN7SwIiLivWe26DA","children":[{"id":"242","parent":"241","text":"Barthel (ABVD):","guid":"aKTdHxezpZtYECajBVINjQ","children":[{"id":"243","parent":"242","text":"Mide la independencia en actividades básicas.","guid":"QkImrHeJfVx93EPOamp4Dg","children":[]},{"id":"244","parent":"242","text":"Ejemplo: Comer solo, moverse, higiene personal, control de esfínteres.","guid":"KhvJiD148A5PVltFZNkJWA","children":[]},{"id":"245","parent":"242","text":"Clasificación:","guid":"c9xHFE3rDYd2GOO7SJ584g","children":[{"id":"246","parent":"245","text":"Leve: Barthel > 75.","guid":"f4Vx8A5HZLcClJ8WRBoejA","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"245","text":"Moderada: Barthel 35-75.","guid":"U7MSbGf8he5IX1jTH4cQPg","children":[]},{"id":"248","parent":"245","text":"Severa: Barthel < 35 (n).","guid":"TwwRoCwhAn9obQiDOt_t8w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"249","parent":"241","text":"Lawton y Brody (AIVD):","guid":"Jp7MRCdorhM34gNHD0OpYw","children":[{"id":"250","parent":"249","text":"Mide la independencia en actividades instrumentales.","guid":"PxxTrg_yKesUlbbwAV56Ww","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"249","text":"Ejemplo: Manejar finanzas, tomar medicamentos, usar transporte público (n).","guid":"B3unRxJx-r5ryPJpMZdw0A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"252","parent":"222","text":"Factores de Riesgo para la\\NPérdida de Funcionalidad","guid":"LJbCcX7bbphP0cx9C0lr0g","children":[{"id":"253","parent":"252","text":"Enfermedades crónicas → Mal controladas afectan la funcionalidad.","guid":"T-rqzDsfTa4WcHooT3BcvQ","children":[]},{"id":"254","parent":"252","text":"Hospitalizaciones → Pérdida funcional frecuente tras una hospitalización, especialmente no programada.","guid":"SWayZhkFGT8TintJHRnE0g","children":[]},{"id":"255","parent":"252","text":"Aislamiento social y deprivación sensorial (no uso de audífonos/lentes).","guid":"AQGfLVvp1Bw8oNURUA2wzg","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"252","text":"Síndromes geriátricos → Incontinencia, sarcopenia, fragilidad → Aumentan riesgo de pérdida funcional (n).","guid":"CArWmyUN3ZQK7Z7Be-cdrw","children":[]}]},{"id":"257","parent":"222","text":"Fragilidad:","guid":"Mc75kxXDj7xyBuvPCdBiIQ","children":[{"id":"258","parent":"257","text":"Paciente con baja reserva fisiológica → Vulnerable a caídas, fracturas, y pérdida funcional.","guid":"cvjrGwEGgnxEhZqSGZe3Xw","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"257","text":"Ejemplo: Sarcopenia → Falta de fuerza muscular.","guid":"DFnHxD1xF7No6f6ZE9VvDA","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"257","text":"Todos los síndromes geriátricos están asociados a un mayor o menor riesgo de pérdida funcional (n).","guid":"T-MSclSy8QJFbN_cH839Pg","children":[]}]},{"id":"261","parent":"222","text":"Factores protectores:","guid":"ZqLxvFSriXxUyrXLOIjWOQ","children":[{"id":"262","parent":"261","text":"Red de apoyo → Familia y cuidadores.","guid":"D9I-sVvdWgRvPln7WTjxFw","children":[]},{"id":"263","parent":"261","text":"Escolaridad → Factor no modificable, pero protector.","guid":"dOJzQwLI1UV2UrXpdeQScQ","children":[]},{"id":"264","parent":"261","text":"Ejercicio → Ejemplo: Yoga, hidroterapia (n).","guid":"XrKpYTLzivpF8cM_Zr1__Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"265","parent":"222","text":"Intervención para Prevenir\\NPérdida Funcional","guid":"e9XBujlcwNUy3etFH2eX0g","children":[{"id":"266","parent":"265","text":"Ventana de\\Nintervención:","guid":"WAFojlDfYgBipJ2sSvpTqg","children":[{"id":"267","parent":"266","text":"Paciente postrado con demencia avanzada → Baja capacidad de recuperación funcional.","guid":"UeXkfCcqOD5kkgsJelUVDA","children":[]},{"id":"268","parent":"266","text":"Pacientes frágiles o con dependencia moderada → Mayor posibilidad de recuperar o prevenir pérdida funcional (n).","guid":"I5HWGA1ta8xh4JlLL-ud3A","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"269","parent":"0","text":"Evaluación Geriátrica\\NIntegral (EGI)","guid":"St6DgErKl-RDwQzoGsGV8g","children":[{"id":"270","parent":"269","text":"Definición:","guid":"H32I5wkt7MQ6j5MwL0_HmA","children":[{"id":"271","parent":"270","text":"Instrumento diagnóstico y terapéutico para identificar factores de riesgo de pérdida funcional.","guid":"RsosoRS-hJBPUzWvEaiwIQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"272","parent":"269","text":"Involucra:","guid":"EMfGcDbfJaNbOzAxPV6I4Q","children":[{"id":"273","parent":"272","text":"Diagnóstico.","guid":"X4kcdRMUQpcsakYTfwalXA","children":[]},{"id":"274","parent":"272","text":"Plan de acción y metas terapéuticas (n).","guid":"HEIvXGb52UQuVmz0AU12JQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"275","parent":"269","text":"Componentes\\Nde la EGI:","guid":"NbqUOysM_K9Ip_SzZ4mNzg","children":[{"id":"276","parent":"275","text":"Biomédico (medicina tradicional).","guid":"QNCMazqu4INxWe_wJ3N-KA","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"275","text":"Mental (cognición y estado de ánimo).","guid":"D1pp_0Ykpbtf_FRhCzAruQ","children":[]},{"id":"278","parent":"275","text":"Social (red de apoyo).","guid":"f4FmkBLaP6Yql8OMRkuTMg","children":[]},{"id":"279","parent":"275","text":"Funcional (capacidad actual del paciente) (n).","guid":"J5jEN3nq-TtX9ENTByHgrA","children":[]}]},{"id":"280","parent":"269","text":"Enfoque\\Nmultidisciplinario:","guid":"DP870gReiWcGKIYIKUFrLg","children":[{"id":"281","parent":"280","text":"Colaboración con la familia/cuidador.","guid":"a1hiqzR-8vwqjuFTfCApGw","children":[]},{"id":"282","parent":"280","text":"Necesidad de trabajar en equipo (médico, kinesiólogo, farmacéutico, etc.) para lograr mejores resultados (n).","guid":"a14YnwXKEYU5frH8IRis2g","children":[]}]},{"id":"283","parent":"269","text":"Cuándo No\\NRealizar la EGI","guid":"MNcONAImpq8Iojqpcaeanw","children":[{"id":"284","parent":"283","text":"Pacientes terminales o\\Nseveramente postrados:","guid":"C_GszwH34HcF7coXM4pxBg","children":[{"id":"285","parent":"284","text":"La EGI no es útil en casos donde la recuperación funcional no es posible.","guid":"PNWHMnn8KpkZGxjHTC_xMQ","children":[]},{"id":"286","parent":"284","text":"En estos casos, se debe enfocar en cuidados paliativos (n).","guid":"QCDQVHkXbShXYBzrP6I25Q","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"287","parent":"0","text":"Importancia del Ejercicio\\Nen el Adulto Mayor","guid":"L90MVmIthdVhVrv3TT4wYw","children":[{"id":"288","parent":"287","text":"Ejercicio → Crucial a cualquier edad.","guid":"LTBOLF4cmcB54im7Gd6nzQ","children":[]},{"id":"289","parent":"287","text":"Mejora la funcionalidad y calidad de vida.","guid":"Id8o5mY5xpkRbgyYMKu51w","children":[]},{"id":"290","parent":"287","text":"Menos difícil si se inicia a edades más tempranas (n).","guid":"Bb-7ZmQFrUFhJdD-Mhq6cg","children":[]}]},{"id":"291","parent":"0","text":"Movilidad y\\NFuerza Muscular","guid":"","children":[{"id":"292","parent":"291","text":"Movilidad:","guid":"e-LZsl3iDWo6rFGyCOIVhA","children":[{"id":"293","parent":"292","text":"La marcha lenta (< 0.8 m/s) es un factor pronóstico de mayor mortalidad.","guid":"YkCW0UDU17oyI4CzTZj5fA","children":[]},{"id":"294","parent":"292","text":"Evaluar velocidad de marcha con test de caminata de 4 metros (n).","guid":"dVPKtlyyYgZJuSKXYLHjVQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"295","parent":"291","text":"Fuerza muscular:","guid":"YnxziwM31JMBypAvE1OBvw","children":[{"id":"296","parent":"295","text":"Medida con dinamómetro o el test de levantarse de la silla (cinco veces).","guid":"BV57QwpsytgE-xxfQjQCdQ","children":[]},{"id":"297","parent":"295","text":"Tiempo > 15 segundos indica sarcopenia y mayor riesgo de caídas y fracturas (n).","guid":"BGj1cR4WNSYOY_OnRInFxg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"298","parent":"0","text":"Caídas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"299","parent":"298","text":"Prevalencia:","guid":"Fy2iT2XEEJIEK_yrIx9PHg","children":[{"id":"300","parent":"299","text":"50% de personas > 80 años se caen.","guid":"Z7vxCQoZxsJWqcAkY57Kuw","children":[]},{"id":"301","parent":"299","text":"10% de estas caídas resultan en daño → La mitad queda con pérdida funcional (n).","guid":"Z_vULBFWEdZsgOA_Sjxq_g","children":[]}]},{"id":"302","parent":"298","text":"Prevención:","guid":"UirpkB6kYPIX1WR6R360Rg","children":[{"id":"303","parent":"302","text":"Intervenciones efectivas como Tai Chi y modificaciones ambientales (e.g., barandas) (n).","guid":"e1bC-WGOhxIoMJebXdM2hA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"304","parent":"0","text":"Fragilidad y\\NEvaluación","guid":"ZMZbpSn7J8pxJrhEaiTW6A","children":[{"id":"305","parent":"304","text":"Fragilidad:","guid":"NGfyo3Yh1KMsWNleONDoFA","children":[{"id":"306","parent":"305","text":"Estado de baja reserva fisiológica → Prevalente en hasta el 60% de los pacientes que sufren fracturas de cadera.","guid":"FDgJyTq8zQV9Wq3aK2WsGA","children":[]},{"id":"307","parent":"305","text":"Mayor riesgo de complicaciones posquirúrgicas y mortalidad (n).","guid":"IIDdlwGGqoVOhPs2CDzOoA","children":[]}]},{"id":"308","parent":"304","text":"Evaluación:","guid":"C6BxRyUuu1pr25lbc5xFdA","children":[{"id":"309","parent":"308","text":"Criterios de Fried y FRAIL son herramientas estándar para medir fragilidad.","guid":"NoTNMFhceZo92LByCK-2wA","children":[]},{"id":"310","parent":"308","text":"Velocidad de marcha y fuerza prensil son también marcadores clave de fragilidad (n).","guid":"dwDajVWuFOxQLmsGcledhg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"311","parent":"0","text":"Optimización de\\NMedicación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"312","parent":"311","text":"Uso inapropiado de\\Nmedicamentos:","guid":"Nzyb_nhfAqFQKtQKHAL3pA","children":[{"id":"313","parent":"312","text":"Común en pacientes institucionalizados o con múltiples comorbilidades.","guid":"IloqbEFRjE4GJ86MVsIdDw","children":[]},{"id":"314","parent":"312","text":"Ajuste y optimización de fármacos es esencial en geriatría (n).","guid":"N3Ng8TKAp-oPkwUjS6tquw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"315","parent":"0","text":"Evaluación Cognitiva\\Ny Ánimo","guid":"bT107wztsv53ERbTDb5Shg","children":[{"id":"316","parent":"315","text":"Cognición:","guid":"DnRdg0WWEgoV-yEmGhTOyw","children":[{"id":"317","parent":"316","text":"Mini Mental y MOCA son herramientas para medir deterioro cognitivo.","guid":"asTNZAHWuoENsRQ_IUmalQ","children":[]},{"id":"318","parent":"316","text":"Uso de MOCA en pacientes con mayor nivel educativo, Mini Mental en pacientes con menor escolaridad (n).","guid":"WjM0HEuJxLEp-VFVUTQOqQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"319","parent":"315","text":"Depresión:","guid":"ITfZnXonvFxDi6wvWHR1nA","children":[{"id":"320","parent":"319","text":"Muy prevalente en adultos mayores (hasta un 26%).","guid":"coa-_RO2gDl0d21AFODpaQ","children":[]},{"id":"321","parent":"319","text":"Pregunta única: \"¿Se siente deprimida?\" → Alta sensibilidad para detectar depresión (n).","guid":"VQgMiHqfO8xrowZ4DHtteQ","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":321,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/General","filename":"Clase introducción-2024","id":"map_709","resolved_references":[]}